     Key factors to consider:
     1. Team constraints: 6 people, no dedicated infrastructure engineer, no Kafka experience
     2. Already running Redis in production
     3. Must deliver value within 2 weeks
     4. Budget constraints - can't afford managed Confluent Cloud
